</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Name for the receiving thread of the client. Setting this NULL will result as default name of &quot;coap_client&quot;.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>int Zero on success, otherwise a negative error code. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
